A workaround for now would be to pass the arguments to gdb directly instead of using a the launch config's `args` field, like so:
```json
"setupCommands": [
  {
    "description": "Set command line arguments",
    "text": "-gdb-set args ${input:commandLineArgs}",
    "ignoreFailures": true
  }
]
```

Or if using static text,
```json
"setupCommands": [
  {
    "description": "Set command line arguments",
    "text": "-gdb-set args arg1 arg2 arg3 arg4",
    "ignoreFailures": true
  }
]
```

